.TH SERIAL-TERM 1 "2026-05-08" "SerialTerm 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
serial-term \- GTK4 serial terminal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B serial-term
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B SerialTerm
is a GTK4/Libadwaita desktop terminal for serial communication.
It provides configurable serial parameters, ANSI terminal display, log export,
themes, persistent JSON settings, and integrated conversion tools.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/serial-term/settings.json
Persistent user settings.
.SH NOTES
To access serial ports without root on Debian-based systems, add the user to the
.B dialout
group, then log out and log back in.
